title: Sentimental Journey
description: a/d) "Sentimental Journey": Two vignettes, one large, one small, alternating vertically. The large scene contains three figures in period costume. The figures appear as if on stage, surrounded by objects. Behind is a tree laden with Spanish moss. Four different colorways of the same design; e) "African Jungle": Designed by Zue Martin. Motifs are jungle animals, including elephant, crocodile, giraffe, ostrich, lion and a pair of monkeys in a tree. Other exotic plants are also interspersed. Printed in pastel shades of pink, blue, green and red on white ground.
